{"tid":471272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學直播李飛講話 學生斥無謂","createTime":"2017-11-17T06:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T07:47:18.000Z","uid":101994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88d64874763b6d64646a00468a5d0d0e327c43ee","tid":471272,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會主任李飛抵港出席基本法研討會，發表長達近一小時的演講，當中本港有五十間中學安排學生收看直播。<br />\n<br />\n其中有參與直播的獅子會中學，當中校方安排共四班、大約一百名分別來自中三、中五，以及中六學生參與。會後有參與學生表示，研討會有助她了解基本法與憲法關係。亦有學生指，李飛能夠解答通識科老師解釋不到的問題。<br />\n<br />\n但另一邊廂，有參與學生則大唱反調，認為研討會以普通話為主，加上本身對政治不熟悉，令他難以吸收當中內容，同時亦有中四學生指，雖然今次無份參與直播，但認為有關安排無謂，若未來校方再舉辧同類型活動，自己都不會有意參與。<br />\n<br />\n而校長林日豐就表示，由於今次研討會對象不是針對學生，加上題目屬於嚴肅課題，令學生未必能夠容易投入，但認為，有關安排屬體驗式學習，亦是一個學習過程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/lifetvnews/videos/463884160679084/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flifetvnews%2Fvideos%2F463884160679084%2F&d=BMeVM3TIdM2uoKT7xN9I%2B0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=91a5966b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/lifetvnews/videos/463884160679084/</a>"},{"pid":"e618b682b3ebe8a3d493892fcba85bc52b603000","tid":471272,"uid":101994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"啲中學校長真係好嘔心<br />\n搵埋晒啲學生做媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fed4cdb58f6dc9de9efb10e552c3cb6897c685","tid":471272,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\